snippet.title: I Need Space - Official Trailer | Game Devs of Color Expo 2024
snippet.description: Get a new look at the sci-fi world, gameplay, and more of I Need Space in this trailer for the upcoming adventure game. In I Need Space, travel across the universe with your nebulous companion the Cosmicat, together rewriting stars, revitalizing planets, and discovering the cosmic truth behind the apocalypse. I Need Space will be available on PC.
